  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a large skillet over medium heat.",
    "Add minced garlic and sauté until fragrant, about 1 minute.",
    "Add diced tomatoes and bell peppers to the pan. Cook for another 5 minutes.",
    "Stir in halved cherry tomatoes, sliced green olives, and basil leaves. Continue cooking for an additional 3-4 minutes or until all vegetables are soft.",
